channel.title: [ RS2 ][ SRL ] Seers Flaxor + Bank Auto Colors
channel.description:
[b]THIS IS NOT MY SCRIPT[/b]
I was looking around and i noticed a lot of people are always asking for a flax picker so i decided to post the one i use.
It does every thing automaticly all you do is run the script with your character standing in seers bank with one flax in his inventory (this is withought having set colors or anything) and it can be logged off or in
then when you run the script it asks you your username and password (so it can log back off and on)
and it asks you how long you want to run the script before taking a break and how long you want to take a break for. it can also detect mods. anyways here it is.
[b]THERE WERE LOTS OF QUESTIONS SO SCROLL DOWN FOR A PICTURE GUIDE TO GETTING IT STARTED[/b]
